04787 // Wrap the EnumValue enum into a struct for the purpose
04788 // of overloading assignment and comparison operators for
04789 // GLenum interchangeability.
04790 
04791 struct Enum
04792 {
04793   inline Enum() : v(RGL_NONE) {}
04794 
04795   inline Enum(const GLenum v) { operator=(v); }
04796 
04797   inline Enum &operator=(const GLenum other)
04798   {
04799     v = static_cast<EnumValue>(other);
04800     return *this;
04801   }
04802 
04803   inline Enum &operator=(const Enum &other)
04804   {
04805     v = other.v;
04806     return *this;
04807   }
04808 
04809   inline operator GLenum () const
04810   {
04811     return static_cast<GLenum>(v);
04812   }
04813 
04814   inline bool operator==(const GLenum other) const { return v==static_cast<EnumValue>(other); }
04815   inline bool operator!=(const GLenum other) const { return v!=static_cast<EnumValue>(other); }
04816 
04817   private:
04818     EnumValue v;
04819 };
